{"tid":2128123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報：中國吸引力擋不住  美國政府激進反華觸犯很多人","createTime":"2020-07-27T17:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T03:55:22.000Z","uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8511eb3ac308c3aa9a0b1fa623441edf7265f834","tid":2128123,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地《環球時報》發表社評，指擴大對外開放，是中國打破美國對華封堵及「新冷戰」戰略的關鍵。社評說，<strong>美國政府在國內及盟友之間進行的反華動員，觸犯很多人、力量及國家的利益，必然面對阻力，只要中國將開放的政策越做越好，就能對華盛頓激進的反華政策，形成抵制。</strong><br />\n<br />\n社評又說，中國不像中小國家那樣容易被封堵，中國的市場規模已經與美國並駕齊驅，對世界有著擋不住的吸引力，只要中國措施得當，不落入美方設計的陷阱，對外開放的槓杆，要比美方封堵中國的槓杆多得多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540216-20200728.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540216-20200728.htm&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=f00d8ca4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540216-20200728.htm&h=2d298d58\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540216-20200728.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5fd84110631c876e471da8e15bc7816610e874b2","tid":2128123,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但兩黨共識喎"},{"pid":"e2ee2284065d166dba9d1449bd6add54bc060908","tid":2128123,"uid":189564,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:54:18.000Z","msg":"打飛機冠軍<br />\n大陸水災 民怨沸騰<br />\n只係敢怒不敢言"},{"pid":"0c6df5ca0be67122a8265b569501cd90481ee406","tid":2128123,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:56:34.000Z","msg":"係咪又要玩 數國家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我國成日都數啲無人識嘅非洲同太平洋國家嚟大人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a441b00d6